    {
      "bookmarkId": "757876_6_4310-4348",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "4310-4348",
      "markText": "然而，人们所获取的比一秒还短得多的生命延长，远远不及劣质飞机餐对健康的损害。",
      "totalCount": 560,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=757876&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=4310&rangeEnd=4348",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8cd32bd05b90748cdef0f4e?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=4310&rangeEnd=4348"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "757876_6_14232-14301",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "14232-14301",
      "markText": "当一个大质量的恒星消耗完它的核燃料时，它将丧失热量并且收缩。时空将被弯翘得这么厉害以至于产生黑洞。光不能从黑洞逃逸。时间将在黑洞之内终结。",
      "totalCount": 486,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=757876&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=14232&rangeEnd=14301",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8cd32bd05b90748cdef0f4e?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=14232&rangeEnd=14301"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "757876_7_5519-5558",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "5519-5558",
      "markText": "询问在开端之前或者终结之后发生什么是没有任何意义的，因为这种时间是不被定义的。",
      "totalCount": 396,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=757876&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=5519&rangeEnd=5558",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8cd32bd05b90748cdef0f4e?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=5519&rangeEnd=5558"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "757876_6_7079-7123",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "7079-7123",
      "markText": "有人将原子弹归咎于爱因斯坦发现了质能关系；但是这和把飞机失事归咎于牛顿发现了引力很类似。",
      "totalCount": 391,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=757876&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=7079&rangeEnd=7123",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8cd32bd05b90748cdef0f4e?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=7079&rangeEnd=7123"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "757876_6_14944-14996",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "14944-14996",
      "markText": "微小的粒子不再具有确定的位置和速度。相反，粒子的位置被测量得越准确，其速度则被测量得越不准确，反之亦然。",
      "totalCount": 360,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=757876&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=14944&rangeEnd=14996",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8cd32bd05b90748cdef0f4e?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=14944&rangeEnd=14996"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "757876_6_4091-4183",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "4091-4183",
      "markText": "这就需要抛弃一个观念，即存在一个所有钟表都测量的称为时间的普适的量。相反地，每个人都有他或她自己个人的时间。如果两个人处于相对静止状态，则他们的时间就一致，但是他们相互运动时就不一致。",
      "totalCount": 345,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=757876&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=4091&rangeEnd=4183",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8cd32bd05b90748cdef0f4e?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=4091&rangeEnd=4183"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "757876_6_8152-8196",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "8152-8196",
      "markText": "在战争年代里他过着独身生活，避免了家事纠缠，这也许是他在这一段时期科学上多产的一个原因。",
      "totalCount": 336,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=757876&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=8152&rangeEnd=8196",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8cd32bd05b90748cdef0f4e?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=8152&rangeEnd=8196"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "757876_6_1566-1618",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "1566-1618",
      "markText": "他们想象空间充满了所谓“以太”的连续介质。光线和射电讯号是在以太中的波动，如同声音为空气中的压力波一样。",
      "totalCount": 300,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=757876&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1566&rangeEnd=1618",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8cd32bd05b90748cdef0f4e?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1566&rangeEnd=1618"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "757876_5_1081-1096",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1081-1096",
      "markText": "充满希望的旅途胜过终点的到达。",
      "totalCount": 289,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=757876&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1081&rangeEnd=1096",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8cd32bd05b90748cdef0f4e?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1081&rangeEnd=1096"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "757876_6_2473-2510",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "2473-2510",
      "markText": "不管人们在哪个方向上多快地运动，光似乎总是以相同的速率相对于它的所在地运动",
      "totalCount": 288,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=757876&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2473&rangeEnd=2510",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8cd32bd05b90748cdef0f4e?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2473&rangeEnd=2510"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "757876_7_5819-5894",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "5819-5894",
      "markText": "如果人们在时间的相反方向将宇宙膨胀倒溯回去，他会发现宇宙中的全部物质并非都从具有无限密度的一点涌现。这样无限密度的点称为奇点，并且是时间的开端或终结。",
      "totalCount": 272,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=757876&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=5819&rangeEnd=5894",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8cd32bd05b90748cdef0f4e?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=5819&rangeEnd=5894"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "757876_6_4919-4953",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "4919-4953",
      "markText": "他们问道，这是否意味着，万物都是相对的，甚至不存在绝对的道德标准呢？",
      "totalCount": 255,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=757876&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=4919&rangeEnd=4953",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8cd32bd05b90748cdef0f4e?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=4919&rangeEnd=4953"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "757876_6_16018-16038",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "16018-16038",
      "markText": "政治是为当前，而方程却是一种永恒的东西。",
      "totalCount": 255,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=757876&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=16018&rangeEnd=16038",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8cd32bd05b90748cdef0f4e?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=16018&rangeEnd=16038"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "757876_5_1486-1529",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1486-1529",
      "markText": "此外，我要感谢所有让我能过上相当正常生活并从事科学研究的人们。没有他们此书便不能问世。",
      "totalCount": 234,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=757876&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1486&rangeEnd=1529",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8cd32bd05b90748cdef0f4e?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1486&rangeEnd=1529"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "757876_7_13563-13634",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "13563-13634",
      "markText": "自旋越高，使粒子显得相同的旋转所需要的整圈部分就越小。但是以下事实令人印象深刻，存在旋转两整圈才显得相同的粒子，这种粒子被称为具有自旋1/2。",
      "totalCount": 221,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=757876&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=13563&rangeEnd=13634",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8cd32bd05b90748cdef0f4e?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=13563&rangeEnd=13634"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "757876_3_464-531",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "464-531",
      "markText": "我愿意和中国读者分享对黑洞和宇宙学中最近发现的激动。 ——史蒂芬·霍金",
